Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:45.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬉しい楽しいばっかじゃない　自分次第
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ONCE MORE SMILE, TWICE MORE CHIME
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:50.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こっち向いてよダーリン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:59.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}わたしの純愛に気づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:38.74,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之多少的喜欢才算是恋爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.83,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怂是罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:53.55,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}头脑风暴滴滴答答 选一种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.01,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}云隙中一阵细雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.05,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不亚至高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:02.60,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少女心它阴晴不定 可爱且无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.14,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像杂乱无章的钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:12.40,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之多少的喜欢才算是恋爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:16.11,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱着我直到我犯困吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:21.66,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像是科幻片般的白日梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:24.70,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲吻我 打破剧中沉默吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:27.12,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}优柔寡断也好 抱紧我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.79,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胸口闷得难受好难受好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:34.63,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心动无法预测
Comment: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:38.09,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's TRUE FOOL LOVE! Hold me tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:40.38,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼓起勇气来呀 My darling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:45.01,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不止于欢乐和欣喜 都取决于我们自己
Comment: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.31,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ONCE MORE SMILE, TWICE MORE CHIME
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:50.56,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}转过来看着我吧 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:59.95,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}注意到我纯粹的爱呀
